10round decision had the bridge of his nose split by tyson in the 
earlymorning incident outside an allnight clothing boutique 
tyson claimed green was harassing him about their meeting in the 
ring tyson said he reacted to green by instinct 
in his last fight in the ring on june 27 tyson knocked out 
previously unbeaten michael spinks in 91 seconds earning 22 
million 
